Mom's Magic: Fierce, Protective & Soft We’ve always portrayed the relationship that mothers share with their children. Virtues they’d like

come from their own moms. Mother-Daughter Duo The film opens with a mother and daughter in the midst of a banter revolving around her recent success in procuring admission to a prestigious college and the happiness around it.
